[{"title":"Hello World","content":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a href=\"#Quick-Start\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#Create-a-new-post\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Create a new post\"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\"><a href=\"#Run-server\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Run server\"></a>Run server</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\"><a href=\"#Generate-static-files\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Generate static files\"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\"><a href=\"#Deploy-to-remote-sites\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Deploy to remote sites\"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html\">Deployment</a></p>\n","isPage":false,"isDraft":false,"permalink":"http://example.com/2026/03/29/hello-world/"},{"title":"жҲ‘зҡ„з¬¬дёҖзҜҮеҚҡе®ў","content":"<h2 id=\"рҹ‘Ӣ-дҪ еҘҪпјҢдё–з•ҢпјҒ\"><a href=\"#рҹ‘Ӣ-дҪ еҘҪпјҢдё–з•ҢпјҒ\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"рҹ‘Ӣ дҪ еҘҪпјҢдё–з•ҢпјҒ\"></a>рҹ‘Ӣ дҪ еҘҪпјҢдё–з•ҢпјҒ</h2><p>иҝҷжҳҜжҲ‘зҡ„з¬¬дёҖзҜҮеҚҡе®ўж–Үз« пјҢи®°еҪ•дёҖдёӢжҗӯе»әеҚҡе®ўзҡ„иҝҮзЁӢпҪһ<br>26.03.29зӘҒеҸ‘еҘҮжғіжғіеҖҹеҠ©GitHub pagesжҗӯе»әдёҖдёӘдәәеҚҡе®ўпјҢ</p>\n<h3 id=\"рҹҺҜ-жҲ‘еӯҰдјҡдәҶ\"><a href=\"#рҹҺҜ-жҲ‘еӯҰдјҡдәҶ\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"рҹҺҜ жҲ‘еӯҰдјҡдәҶ\"></a>рҹҺҜ жҲ‘еӯҰдјҡдәҶ</h3><p>вңҚпёҸ еҶҷж–Үз« <br>  в”ңв”Җ е‘Ҫд»Өпјҡhexo new post вҖңж ҮйўҳвҖқ<br>  в”ңв”Җ дҪҚзҪ®пјҡsource&#x2F;_posts&#x2F;ж Үйўҳ.md<br>  в””в”Җ еӣҫзүҮпјҡж”ҫ source&#x2F;images&#x2F;пјҢж–Үдёӯз”Ё &#x2F;images&#x2F;xxx.jpg</p>\n<p>рҹ”Қ йў„и§Ҳ<br>  в”ңв”Җ hexo clean<br>  в”ңв”Җ hexo generate<br>  в””в”Җ hexo server вҶ’ <a href=\"http://localhost:4000/\">http://localhost:4000</a></p>\n<p>рҹҡҖ еҸ‘еёғ<br>  в”ңв”Җ git add .          ж·»еҠ жүҖжңүдҝ®ж”№<br>  в”ңв”Җ git commit -m вҖңеӨҮжіЁвҖқ<br>  в”ңв”Җ git push          (жәҗд»Јз ҒвҶ’src еҲҶж”Ҝ)<br>  в””в”Җ hexo d            (зҪ‘з«ҷж–Үд»¶вҶ’main еҲҶж”Ҝ)</p>\n<p>рҹҢҗ и®ҝй—®<br>  в””в”Җ <a href=\"https://yhnz1234.github.io/\">https://yhnz1234.github.io</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"рҹ“ё-жҲӘеӣҫеұ•зӨә\"><a href=\"#рҹ“ё-жҲӘеӣҫеұ•зӨә\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"рҹ“ё жҲӘеӣҫеұ•зӨә\"></a>рҹ“ё жҲӘеӣҫеұ•зӨә</h3><p><img src=\"/images/screenshot-myblog.png\" alt=\"еҚҡе®ўйҰ–йЎө\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"рҹ’ӯ-е°Ҹз»“\"><a href=\"#рҹ’ӯ-е°Ҹз»“\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"рҹ’ӯ е°Ҹз»“\"></a>рҹ’ӯ е°Ҹз»“</h3><p>иҷҪз„¶иҝҮзЁӢжңүзӮ№жӣІжҠҳпјҢдҪҶзңӢеҲ°зҪ‘з«ҷдёҠзәҝзҡ„йӮЈдёҖеҲ»пјҢдёҖеҲҮйғҪеҖјеҫ—пјҒ</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>жңӘжқҘдјҡеңЁиҝҷйҮҢеҲҶдә«жӣҙеӨҡеӯҰд№ е’Ңз”ҹжҙ»зҡ„еҶ…е®№пјҢж¬ўиҝҺе…іжіЁпҪһ</p>\n</blockquote>\n","isPage":false,"isDraft":false,"permalink":"http://example.com/2026/03/30/%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"}]